WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
The signal: breakout close.

00:03.000 --> 00:06.000
This is our trade signal.

00:06.000 --> 00:09.500
Not a guess or wick.

00:09.500 --> 00:13.500
A clean Asian box has formed.

00:13.500 --> 00:18.500
Price closes outside on one hour.

00:18.500 --> 00:23.500
The marker prints BREAKOUT CLOSE.

00:23.500 --> 00:27.500
The candle has finished.

00:27.500 --> 00:31.500
The next step is not chasing.

00:31.500 --> 00:35.500
The marker gives the plan.

00:35.500 --> 00:39.500
EXEC shows planned entry price.

00:39.500 --> 00:43.000
Red zone is the stop.

00:43.000 --> 00:46.500
Green zone is the target.

00:46.500 --> 00:49.500
Prices are printed inside.

00:49.500 --> 00:53.500
Right edge is the time exit.

00:53.500 --> 00:57.500
Target, stop, or time ends it.

00:57.500 --> 01:00.500
Scroll forward on the real recording.

01:00.500 --> 01:01.700
Clean box. Checklist passed.

01:01.700 --> 01:02.900
One-hour breakout close.

01:02.900 --> 01:03.800
Trade managed by the zones.
